diff --git a/src/data/controllers/Map/GetProjects.controller.js b/src/data/controllers/Map/GetProjects.controller.js
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..89c0384a
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/data/controllers/Map/GetProjects.controller.js
@@ -0,0 +1,32 @@
+import { GetProjectsService } from '../../services';
+
+export class GetProjectsController {
+  async handle(req, res) {
+    try {
+      const { nm_project, nm_city, id_category, tp_project_phase } = req.query;
+
+      const service = new GetProjectsService();
+
+      const response = await service.execute({
+        nm_project,
+        nm_city,
+        id_category,
+        tp_project_phase,
+      });
+
+      if (response.error)
+        return res.status(400).json({
+          error: response.error,
+        });
+
+      return res.status(200).json({
+        projects: response.projects,
+      });
+    } catch (err) {
+      console.log(err);
+      return res.status(500).json({
+        error: 'Ocorreu um problema interno',
+      });
+    }
+  }
+}

diff --git a/src/data/services/Map/FindCoordinates.js b/src/data/services/Map/FindCoordinates.js
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..5a5e8357
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/data/services/Map/FindCoordinates.js
@@ -0,0 +1,355 @@
+import Sequelize, { Op } from 'sequelize';
+
+import {
+  Project,
+  Project_phase,
+  Product,
+  Product_history,
+  City,
+  Region,
+  Location,
+  Polygon_area,
+  Category,
+  Timelapse_Coordinates,
+  Media_timelapse,
+} from '../../database/models';
+import { calculateHour } from '../../../utils/calculateHour';
+
+const formatValue = value =>
+  value.toLocaleString('pt-BR', {
+    minimumFractionDigits: 2,
+    maximumFractionDigits: 2,
+  });
+
+export class GetProjectsService {
+  async execute({ nm_project, nm_city, id_category, tp_project_phase }) {
+    const projects = await Project.findAndCountAll({
+      attributes: [
+        'id_project',
+        'nm_project',
+        'cd_sei',
+        'cd_priority',
+        'qt_m2',
+        'vl_estimated',
+        'vl_bid',
+        'vl_contract',
+        'tx_description',
+      ],
+
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Category,
+          as: 'category',
+          attributes: ['nm_category', 'id_category'],
+        },
+        {
+          model: City,
+          as: 'city',
+          attributes: ['nm_city'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Region,
+              as: 'region',
+              attributes: ['nm_region'],
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Location,
+          as: 'location',
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Polygon_area,
+              as: 'polygon_area',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    const Data = [];
+
+    await Promise.all(
+      projects.rows.map(async project => {
+        const ID_PROJECT_PHASES = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+          result => result.dataValues.id_project_phase
+        );
+
+        if (ID_PROJECT_PHASES.length === 0) {
+          Data.push({
+            id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+            nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+            cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+            tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+            nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+            qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+            nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+            id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+            cd_priority:
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+            value:
+              (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+              (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+              (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+              '',
+            project_phase: '',
+            timelapse: [],
+            phaseCompletion: '',
+            location:
+              project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                ? project.dataValues.location
+                : '',
+            polygon_area: project.dataValues.polygon_area,
+          });
+        } else {
+          const products = await Product.findAll({
+            where: {
+              id_project_phase: {
+                [Op.in]: ID_PROJECT_PHASES,
+              },
+            },
+          });
+
+          if (products.length > 0) {
+            const ID_PRODUCTS = products.map(
+              product => product.dataValues.id_product
+            );
+
+            const findLastRecord = await Product_history.findAll({
+              attributes: [
+                [
+                  Sequelize.fn('MAX', Sequelize.col('id_product_history')),
+                  'id_product_history',
+                ],
+              ],
+              group: Sequelize.col('id_product'),
+              raw: true,
+              having: {
+                id_product: {
+                  [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCTS,
+                },
+              },
+            });
+
+            const values = findLastRecord.map(
+              ({ id_product_history }) => id_product_history
+            );
+
+            const productHistories = await Product_history.findAll({
+              where: {
+                [Op.and]: {
+                  id_product_history: {
+                    [Op.in]: values,
+                  },
+                  cd_status: {
+                    [Op.gt]: 0,
+                  },
+                },
+              },
+              include: [
+                {
+                  model: Product,
+                  as: 'product',
+                },
+              ],
+            });
+
+            if (productHistories.length > 0) {
+              const projectPhaseWithHistories = productHistories.map(
+                ph => ph.dataValues.product.dataValues.id_project_phase
+              );
+
+              const reducedArray = projectPhaseWithHistories.reduce(
+                (acc, curr) => {
+                  if (acc.length === 0)
+                    acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+                  else if (
+                    acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr) === -1
+                  )
+                    acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+                  else
+                    ++acc[acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr)]
+                      .count;
+                  return acc;
+                },
+                []
+              );
+
+              const sort = reducedArray.sort((a, b) => b.count - a.count);
+
+              const project_phase = await Project_phase.findOne({
+                where: {
+                  id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+                },
+                include: [
+                  {
+                    model: Timelapse_Coordinates,
+                    as: 'timelapse',
+                    include: [
+                      {
+                        model: Media_timelapse,
+                        as: 'media_timelapse',
+                      },
+                    ],
+                  },
+                ],
+              });
+
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+                nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+                cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+                nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+                tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+                qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+                nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+                id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+                cd_priority:
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+                value:
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                  '',
+                project_phase: project_phase.dataValues.nm_project_phase,
+                timelapse: project_phase.dataValues.timelapse,
+                tp_project_phase: project_phase.dataValues.tp_project_phase,
+
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            } else {
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+                nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+                cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+                nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+                tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+                qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+                nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+                id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+                cd_priority:
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+                value:
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                  '',
+                project_phase: '',
+                timelapse: [],
+                phaseCompletion: '',
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            }
+          } else {
+            Data.push({
+              id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+              nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+              cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+              nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+              tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+              qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+              nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+              id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+              cd_priority:
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+              value:
+                (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                '',
+              project_phase: '',
+              timelapse: [],
+              phaseCompletion: '',
+              location:
+                project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                  ? project.dataValues.location
+                  : '',
+              polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+            });
+          }
+        }
+      })
+    );
+
+    const res = Data.filter(item => item.location);
+
+    const filter = {
+      ...(nm_project && { nm_project }),
+      ...(nm_city && { nm_city }),
+      ...(id_category && { id_category: Number(id_category) }),
+      ...(tp_project_phase && { tp_project_phase: Number(tp_project_phase) }),
+    };
+
+    const kek = res.filter(item => {
+      // eslint-disable-next-line no-restricted-syntax
+      for (const key in filter) {
+        if (!item[key]) return false;
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'string') {
+          if (
+            item[key] === undefined ||
+            (item[key] && !item[key].includes(filter[key]))
+          )
+            return false;
+        }
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'number') {
+          if (item[key] === undefined || item[key] !== filter[key])
+            return false;
+        }
+      }
+      return true;
+    });
+
+    return {
+      projects: kek,
+    };
+  }
+}

+import Sequelize, { Op } from 'sequelize';
+
+import {
+  Project,
+  Project_phase,
+  Product,
+  Product_history,
+  City,
+  Region,
+  Location,
+  Polygon_area,
+  Category,
+  Timelapse_Coordinates,
+  Media_timelapse,
+} from '../../database/models';
+import { calculateHour } from '../../../utils/calculateHour';
+
+const formatValue = value =>
+  value.toLocaleString('pt-BR', {
+    minimumFractionDigits: 2,
+    maximumFractionDigits: 2,
+  });
+
+export class GetProjectsService {
+  async execute({ nm_project, nm_city, id_category, tp_project_phase }) {
+    const projects = await Project.findAndCountAll({
+      attributes: [
+        'id_project',
+        'nm_project',
+        'cd_sei',
+        'cd_priority',
+        'qt_m2',
+        'vl_estimated',
+        'vl_bid',
+        'vl_contract',
+        'tx_description',
+      ],
+
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Category,
+          as: 'category',
+          attributes: ['nm_category', 'id_category'],
+        },
+        {
+          model: City,
+          as: 'city',
+          attributes: ['nm_city'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Region,
+              as: 'region',
+              attributes: ['nm_region'],
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Location,
+          as: 'location',
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Polygon_area,
+              as: 'polygon_area',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    const Data = [];
+
+    await Promise.all(
+      projects.rows.map(async project => {
+        const ID_PROJECT_PHASES = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+          result => result.dataValues.id_project_phase
+        );
+
+        if (ID_PROJECT_PHASES.length === 0) {
+          Data.push({
+            id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+            nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+            cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+            tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+            nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+            qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+            nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+            id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+            cd_priority:
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+              (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+            value:
+              (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+              (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+              (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+              '',
+            project_phase: '',
+            timelapse: [],
+            phaseCompletion: '',
+            location:
+              project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                ? project.dataValues.location
+                : '',
+            polygon_area: project.dataValues.polygon_area,
+          });
+        } else {
+          const products = await Product.findAll({
+            where: {
+              id_project_phase: {
+                [Op.in]: ID_PROJECT_PHASES,
+              },
+            },
+          });
+
+          if (products.length > 0) {
+            const ID_PRODUCTS = products.map(
+              product => product.dataValues.id_product
+            );
+
+            const findLastRecord = await Product_history.findAll({
+              attributes: [
+                [
+                  Sequelize.fn('MAX', Sequelize.col('id_product_history')),
+                  'id_product_history',
+                ],
+              ],
+              group: Sequelize.col('id_product'),
+              raw: true,
+              having: {
+                id_product: {
+                  [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCTS,
+                },
+              },
+            });
+
+            const values = findLastRecord.map(
+              ({ id_product_history }) => id_product_history
+            );
+
+            const productHistories = await Product_history.findAll({
+              where: {
+                [Op.and]: {
+                  id_product_history: {
+                    [Op.in]: values,
+                  },
+                  cd_status: {
+                    [Op.gt]: 0,
+                  },
+                },
+              },
+              include: [
+                {
+                  model: Product,
+                  as: 'product',
+                },
+              ],
+            });
+
+            if (productHistories.length > 0) {
+              const projectPhaseWithHistories = productHistories.map(
+                ph => ph.dataValues.product.dataValues.id_project_phase
+              );
+
+              const reducedArray = projectPhaseWithHistories.reduce(
+                (acc, curr) => {
+                  if (acc.length === 0)
+                    acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+                  else if (
+                    acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr) === -1
+                  )
+                    acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+                  else
+                    ++acc[acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr)]
+                      .count;
+                  return acc;
+                },
+                []
+              );
+
+              const sort = reducedArray.sort((a, b) => b.count - a.count);
+
+              const project_phase = await Project_phase.findOne({
+                where: {
+                  id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+                },
+                include: [
+                  {
+                    model: Timelapse_Coordinates,
+                    as: 'timelapse',
+                    include: [
+                      {
+                        model: Media_timelapse,
+                        as: 'media_timelapse',
+                      },
+                    ],
+                  },
+                ],
+              });
+
+              const getProductsFromProjectPhase =
+                sort.length > 0 &&
+                (await Product.findAll({
+                  where: {
+                    id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+                  },
+                }));
+
+              const productsZ = getProductsFromProjectPhase.map(product => ({
+                id_product: product.id_product,
+                product_name: product.nm_product,
+                duration: calculateHour({
+                  max: product.qt_maximum_hours,
+                  min: product.qt_minimum_hours,
+                  prov: product.qt_probable_hours,
+                  value: product.tp_required_action,
+                }),
+              }));
+
+              const productSumDuration =
+                productsZ.length > 0 &&
+                productsZ.reduce((acc, curr) => {
+                  return acc + curr.duration;
+                }, 0);
+
+              const productHistoriesConcluded = await Product_history.findAll({
+                where: {
+                  [Op.and]: {
+                    id_product_history: {
+                      [Op.in]: values,
+                    },
+                    cd_status: {
+                      [Op.eq]: 5,
+                    },
+                  },
+                },
+                attributes: ['id_product'],
+                include: [
+                  {
+                    model: Product,
+                    as: 'product',
+                  },
+                ],
+              });
+
+              const productHistoriesConcluded2 = productHistoriesConcluded.map(
+                productHistory => ({
+                  id_product: productHistory.dataValues.product.id_product,
+                  product_name: productHistory.dataValues.product.nm_product,
+                  duration: calculateHour({
+                    max: productHistory.dataValues.product.qt_maximum_hours,
+                    min: productHistory.dataValues.product.qt_minimum_hours,
+                    prov: productHistory.dataValues.product.qt_probable_hours,
+                    value: productHistory.dataValues.product.tp_required_action,
+                  }),
+                })
+              );
+
+              const productHistoriesConcluded3 = productHistoriesConcluded2.reduce(
+                (acc, curr) => {
+                  return acc + curr.duration;
+                },
+                0
+              );
+
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+                nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+                cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+                nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+                tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+                qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+                nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+                id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+                cd_priority:
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+                value:
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                  '',
+                project_phase: project_phase.dataValues.nm_project_phase,
+                timelapse: project_phase.dataValues.timelapse,
+                tp_project_phase: project_phase.dataValues.tp_project_phase,
+
+                phaseCompletion: `${(
+                  (productHistoriesConcluded3 / productSumDuration) *
+                  100
+                ).toFixed(2)}%`,
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            } else {
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+                nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+                cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+                nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+                tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+                qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+                nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+                id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+                cd_priority:
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                  (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+                value:
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                  (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                    formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                  '',
+                project_phase: '',
+                timelapse: [],
+                phaseCompletion: '',
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            }
+          } else {
+            Data.push({
+              id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+
+              nm_project: project.dataValues.nm_project,
+              cd_sei: project.dataValues.cd_sei,
+              nm_city: project.dataValues.city.nm_city,
+              tx_description: project.dataValues.tx_description || '',
+
+              qt_m2: project.dataValues.qt_m2 || '',
+              nm_category: project.dataValues.category.nm_category,
+              id_category: project.dataValues.category.id_category,
+              cd_priority:
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 1 && 'Baixa') ||
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 2 && 'Média') ||
+                (project.dataValues.cd_priority === 3 && 'Alta'),
+              value:
+                (project.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+                (project.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+                (project.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+                  formatValue(project.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+                '',
+              project_phase: '',
+              timelapse: [],
+              phaseCompletion: '',
+              location:
+                project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                  ? project.dataValues.location
+                  : '',
+              polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+            });
+          }
+        }
+      })
+    );
+
+    const res = Data.filter(item => item.location);
+
+    const filter = {
+      ...(nm_project && { nm_project }),
+      ...(nm_city && { nm_city }),
+      ...(id_category && { id_category: Number(id_category) }),
+      ...(tp_project_phase && { tp_project_phase: Number(tp_project_phase) }),
+    };
+
+    const kek = res.filter(item => {
+      // eslint-disable-next-line no-restricted-syntax
+      for (const key in filter) {
+        if (!item[key]) return false;
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'string') {
+          if (
+            item[key] === undefined ||
+            (item[key] && !item[key].includes(filter[key]))
+          )
+            return false;
+        }
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'number') {
+          if (item[key] === undefined || item[key] !== filter[key])
+            return false;
+        }
+      }
+      return true;
+    });
+
+    return {
+      projects: kek,
+    };
+  }
+}

+import Sequelize, { Op } from 'sequelize';
+
+import {
+  Project,
+  Project_phase,
+  Product,
+  Product_history,
+  City,
+  Region,
+  Location,
+  Polygon_area,
+  Category,
+  Timelapse_Coordinates,
+  Media_timelapse,
+} from '../../database/models';
+
+export class GetProjectsCoordinatesService {
+  async execute({ nm_project, nm_city, id_category, tp_project_phase }) {
+    const projects = await Project.findAndCountAll({
+      attributes: [
+        'id_project',
+        'nm_project',
+        'cd_sei',
+        'cd_priority',
+        'qt_m2',
+        'vl_estimated',
+        'vl_bid',
+        'vl_contract',
+        'tx_description',
+      ],
+
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Category,
+          as: 'category',
+          attributes: ['nm_category', 'id_category'],
+        },
+        {
+          model: City,
+          as: 'city',
+          attributes: ['nm_city'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Region,
+              as: 'region',
+              attributes: ['nm_region'],
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Location,
+          as: 'location',
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Polygon_area,
+              as: 'polygon_area',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Timelapse_Coordinates,
+              as: 'timelapse',
+              include: [
+                {
+                  model: Media_timelapse,
+                  as: 'media_timelapse',
+                },
+              ],
+            },
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    const Data = [];
+
+    await Promise.all(
+      projects.rows.map(async project => {
+        const ID_PROJECT_PHASES = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+          result => result.dataValues.id_project_phase
+        );
+
+        if (ID_PROJECT_PHASES.length === 0) {
+          Data.push({
+            id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+            timelapse: [],
+            location:
+              project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                ? project.dataValues.location
+                : '',
+            polygon_area: project.dataValues.polygon_area,
+          });
+        } else {
+          const products = await Product.findAll({
+            where: {
+              id_project_phase: {
+                [Op.in]: ID_PROJECT_PHASES,
+              },
+            },
+          });
+
+          if (products.length > 0) {
+            const ID_PRODUCTS = products.map(
+              product => product.dataValues.id_product
+            );
+
+            const findLastRecord = await Product_history.findAll({
+              attributes: [
+                [
+                  Sequelize.fn('MAX', Sequelize.col('id_product_history')),
+                  'id_product_history',
+                ],
+              ],
+              group: Sequelize.col('id_product'),
+              raw: true,
+              having: {
+                id_product: {
+                  [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCTS,
+                },
+              },
+            });
+
+            const values = findLastRecord.map(
+              ({ id_product_history }) => id_product_history
+            );
+
+            const productHistories = await Product_history.findAll({
+              where: {
+                [Op.and]: {
+                  id_product_history: {
+                    [Op.in]: values,
+                  },
+                  cd_status: {
+                    [Op.gt]: 0,
+                  },
+                },
+              },
+              include: [
+                {
+                  model: Product,
+                  as: 'product',
+                },
+              ],
+            });
+
+            if (productHistories.length > 0) {
+              // const projectPhaseWithHistories = productHistories.map(
+              //   ph => ph.dataValues.product.dataValues.id_project_phase
+              // );
+
+              // const reducedArray = projectPhaseWithHistories.reduce(
+              //   (acc, curr) => {
+              //     if (acc.length === 0)
+              //       acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+              //     else if (
+              //       acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr) === -1
+              //     )
+              //       acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+              //     else
+              //       ++acc[acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr)]
+              //         .count;
+              //     return acc;
+              //   },
+              //   []
+              // );
+
+              // const sort = reducedArray.sort((a, b) => b.count - a.count);
+
+              // const project_phase = await Project_phase.findOne({
+              //   where: {
+              //     id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+              //   },
+              //   include: [
+              //     {
+              //       model: Timelapse_Coordinates,
+              //       as: 'timelapse',
+              //       include: [
+              //         {
+              //           model: Media_timelapse,
+              //           as: 'media_timelapse',
+              //         },
+              //       ],
+              //     },
+              //   ],
+              // });
+
+              const getProjectsPhases = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+                item => item.id_project_phase
+              );
+
+              const getMedias = await Timelapse_Coordinates.findAll({
+                where: {
+                  id_project_phase: {
+                    [Op.in]: getProjectsPhases,
+                  },
+                },
+                include: [
+                  {
+                    required: true,
+                    model: Media_timelapse,
+                    as: 'media_timelapse',
+                  },
+                ],
+              });
+
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+                // timelapse: project_phase.dataValues.timelapse,
+                timelapse: getMedias,
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            } else {
+              Data.push({
+                id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+                timelapse: [],
+                location:
+                  project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                    ? project.dataValues.location
+                    : '',
+                polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+              });
+            }
+          } else {
+            Data.push({
+              id_project: project.dataValues.id_project,
+              timelapse: [],
+              location:
+                project.dataValues.location.length > 0
+                  ? project.dataValues.location
+                  : '',
+              polygon_area: project.dataValues.location.polygon_area,
+            });
+          }
+        }
+      })
+    );
+
+    const res = Data.filter(item => item.location);
+
+    const filter = {
+      ...(nm_project && { nm_project }),
+      ...(nm_city && { nm_city }),
+      ...(id_category && { id_category: Number(id_category) }),
+      ...(tp_project_phase && { tp_project_phase: Number(tp_project_phase) }),
+    };
+
+    const kek = res.filter(item => {
+      // eslint-disable-next-line no-restricted-syntax
+      for (const key in filter) {
+        if (!item[key]) return false;
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'string') {
+          if (
+            item[key] === undefined ||
+            (item[key] && !item[key].includes(filter[key]))
+          )
+            return false;
+        }
+
+        if (typeof item[key] === 'number') {
+          if (item[key] === undefined || item[key] !== filter[key])
+            return false;
+        }
+      }
+      return true;
+    });
+
+    return {
+      projects: kek,
+    };
+  }
+}
diff --git a/src/data/services/Map/GetProjectsDataLocation.service.js b/src/data/services/Map/GetProjectsDataLocation.service.js
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..be55f833
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/data/services/Map/GetProjectsDataLocation.service.js
@@ -0,0 +1,210 @@
+import Sequelize, { Op } from 'sequelize';
+
+import {
+  Project,
+  Project_phase,
+  Product,
+  Product_history,
+  City,
+  Region,
+  Location,
+  Polygon_area,
+  Category,
+} from '../../database/models';
+
+const formatValue = value =>
+  value.toLocaleString('pt-BR', {
+    minimumFractionDigits: 2,
+    maximumFractionDigits: 2,
+  });
+
+export class GetProjectsDataLocationService {
+  async execute({ id_location }) {
+    const projects = await Project.findOne({
+      attributes: [
+        'id_project',
+        'nm_project',
+        'vl_estimated',
+        'vl_bid',
+        'vl_contract',
+        'tx_description',
+      ],
+
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Category,
+          as: 'category',
+          attributes: ['nm_category', 'id_category'],
+        },
+        {
+          model: City,
+          as: 'city',
+          attributes: ['nm_city'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Region,
+              as: 'region',
+              attributes: ['nm_region'],
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Location,
+          as: 'location',
+          where: {
+            id_location,
+          },
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Polygon_area,
+              as: 'polygon_area',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    // PEGAR A FASE ATUAL
+
+    const project = await Project.findOne({
+      where: {
+        id_project: projects.dataValues.id_project,
+      },
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    let project_phase;
+
+    if (project.dataValues.project_phase.length > 0) {
+      /// SETAR OS ID DAS FASES DO PROJETO EM UM ARRAY
+      const ID_PROJECT_PHASES = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+        result => result.dataValues.id_project_phase
+      );
+
+      /// PEGAR OS PRODUTOS REFERENTES AS FASES
+      const products = await Product.findAll({
+        where: {
+          id_project_phase: {
+            [Op.in]: ID_PROJECT_PHASES,
+          },
+        },
+      });
+
+      // SETAR OS ID DOS PRODUTOS EM UM ARRAY
+      const ID_PRODUCTS = products.map(
+        product => product.dataValues.id_product
+      );
+
+      // BUSCAR PELO STATUS ATUAL DE CADA PRODUTO
+      const findLastRecord = await Product_history.findAll({
+        attributes: [
+          [
+            Sequelize.fn('MAX', Sequelize.col('id_product_history')),
+            'id_product_history',
+          ],
+        ],
+        group: Sequelize.col('id_product'),
+        raw: true,
+        having: {
+          id_product: {
+            [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCTS,
+          },
+        },
+      });
+
+      // SETAR OS ID DO HISTORICO DE PRODUTO EM UM ARRAY
+      const ID_PRODUCT_HISTORIES = findLastRecord.map(
+        ({ id_product_history }) => id_product_history
+      );
+
+      const productHistories = await Product_history.findAll({
+        where: {
+          [Op.and]: {
+            id_product_history: {
+              [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCT_HISTORIES,
+            },
+            cd_status: {
+              [Op.gt]: 0,
+            },
+          },
+        },
+        include: [
+          {
+            model: Product,
+            as: 'product',
+          },
+        ],
+      });
+
+      const projectPhaseWithHistories = productHistories.map(
+        ph => ph.dataValues.product.dataValues.id_project_phase
+      );
+
+      const reducedArray = projectPhaseWithHistories.reduce((acc, curr) => {
+        if (acc.length === 0) acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+        else if (acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr) === -1)
+          acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+        else ++acc[acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr)].count;
+        return acc;
+      }, []);
+
+      const sort = reducedArray.sort((a, b) => b.count - a.count);
+
+      project_phase = await Project_phase.findOne({
+        where: {
+          id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+        },
+      });
+    } else {
+      project_phase = false;
+    }
+
+    return {
+      projects: {
+        actual_project_phase: !project_phase
+          ? ''
+          : project_phase.dataValues.nm_project_phase,
+        id_project: projects.dataValues.id_project,
+        tx_description: projects.dataValues.tx_description,
+        nm_project: projects.dataValues.nm_project,
+        nm_category: projects.dataValues.category.dataValues.nm_category,
+        nm_city: projects.dataValues.city.dataValues.nm_city,
+        nu_latitude: projects.dataValues.location[0].dataValues.nu_latitude,
+        nu_longitude: projects.dataValues.location[0].dataValues.nu_longitude,
+        value:
+          (projects.dataValues.vl_contract &&
+            formatValue(projects.dataValues.vl_contract)) ||
+          (projects.dataValues.vl_bid &&
+            formatValue(projects.dataValues.vl_bid)) ||
+          (projects.dataValues.vl_estimated &&
+            formatValue(projects.dataValues.vl_estimated)) ||
+          '',
+      },
+    };
+  }
+}

+import Sequelize, { Op } from 'sequelize';
+import {
+  Project,
+  Project_phase,
+  City,
+  Category,
+  Timelapse_Coordinates,
+  Media_timelapse,
+  Product,
+  Product_history,
+} from '../../database/models';
+
+const formatValue = value =>
+  value.toLocaleString('pt-BR', {
+    minimumFractionDigits: 2,
+    maximumFractionDigits: 2,
+  });
+
+export class GetProjectsDataTimelapseService {
+  async execute({ id_timelapse_coordinates }) {
+    const getTimelapse = await Timelapse_Coordinates.findOne({
+      where: {
+        id_timelapse_coordinates,
+      },
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Media_timelapse,
+          as: 'media_timelapse',
+        },
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Project,
+              as: 'project',
+              include: [
+                {
+                  model: Category,
+                  as: 'category',
+                },
+                {
+                  model: City,
+                  as: 'city',
+                },
+              ],
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    // PEGAR A FASE ATUAL
+
+    const project = await Project.findOne({
+      where: {
+        id_project:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .id_project,
+      },
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Project_phase,
+          as: 'project_phase',
+          attributes: ['id_project_phase', 'nu_order', 'nm_project_phase'],
+          include: [
+            {
+              model: Product,
+              as: 'product',
+            },
+          ],
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    /// SETAR OS ID DAS FASES DO PROJETO EM UM ARRAY
+    const ID_PROJECT_PHASES = project.dataValues.project_phase.map(
+      result => result.dataValues.id_project_phase
+    );
+
+    /// PEGAR OS PRODUTOS REFERENTES AS FASES
+    const products = await Product.findAll({
+      where: {
+        id_project_phase: {
+          [Op.in]: ID_PROJECT_PHASES,
+        },
+      },
+    });
+
+    // SETAR OS ID DOS PRODUTOS EM UM ARRAY
+    const ID_PRODUCTS = products.map(product => product.dataValues.id_product);
+
+    // BUSCAR PELO STATUS ATUAL DE CADA PRODUTO
+    const findLastRecord = await Product_history.findAll({
+      attributes: [
+        [
+          Sequelize.fn('MAX', Sequelize.col('id_product_history')),
+          'id_product_history',
+        ],
+      ],
+      group: Sequelize.col('id_product'),
+      raw: true,
+      having: {
+        id_product: {
+          [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCTS,
+        },
+      },
+    });
+
+    // SETAR OS ID DO HISTORICO DE PRODUTO EM UM ARRAY
+    const ID_PRODUCT_HISTORIES = findLastRecord.map(
+      ({ id_product_history }) => id_product_history
+    );
+
+    const productHistories = await Product_history.findAll({
+      where: {
+        [Op.and]: {
+          id_product_history: {
+            [Op.in]: ID_PRODUCT_HISTORIES,
+          },
+          cd_status: {
+            [Op.gt]: 0,
+          },
+        },
+      },
+      include: [
+        {
+          model: Product,
+          as: 'product',
+        },
+      ],
+    });
+
+    const projectPhaseWithHistories = productHistories.map(
+      ph => ph.dataValues.product.dataValues.id_project_phase
+    );
+
+    const reducedArray = projectPhaseWithHistories.reduce((acc, curr) => {
+      if (acc.length === 0) acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+      else if (acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr) === -1)
+        acc.push({ id_project_phase: curr, count: 1 });
+      else ++acc[acc.findIndex(f => f.id_project_phase === curr)].count;
+      return acc;
+    }, []);
+
+    const sort = reducedArray.sort((a, b) => b.count - a.count);
+
+    const project_phase = await Project_phase.findOne({
+      where: {
+        id_project_phase: sort[0].id_project_phase,
+      },
+    });
+
+    return {
+      projects: {
+        id_timelapse_coordinates:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.id_timelapse_coordinates,
+        ds_coordinates: getTimelapse.dataValues.ds_coordinates,
+        id_project_phase:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.id_project_phase,
+        nm_project_phase:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.nm_project_phase,
+        actual_project_phase: project_phase.dataValues.nm_project_phase,
+        id_project:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .id_project,
+        tx_description:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .tx_description,
+        nm_project:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .nm_project,
+        nm_category:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .category.dataValues.nm_category,
+        nm_city:
+          getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .city.dataValues.nm_city,
+        value:
+          (getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .vl_contract &&
+            formatValue(
+              getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project
+                .dataValues.vl_contract
+            )) ||
+          (getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project.dataValues
+            .vl_bid &&
+            formatValue(
+              getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project

+            formatValue(
+              getTimelapse.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.project
+                .dataValues.vl_estimated
+            )) ||
+          '',
+      },
+    };
+  }

diff --git a/src/data/services/ProjectPhase/FindProjectPhasesWithTimelapse.service.js b/src/data/services/ProjectPhase/FindProjectPhasesWithTimelapse.service.js
new file mode 100644
index 00000000..9adf9beb
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/data/services/ProjectPhase/FindProjectPhasesWithTimelapse.service.js
@@ -0,0 +1,30 @@
+import { TimelapseRepository } from '../../database/repositories';
+
+export class FindProjectPhasesWithTimelapseService {
+  async execute({ id_project }) {
+    const repository = new TimelapseRepository();
+
+    const getTimelapses = await repository.findTimelapseByProjectId({
+      id_project,
+    });
+
+    const getCoordinates = getTimelapses.map(item => {
+      return {
+        id_project_phase:
+          item.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.id_project_phase,
+        nm_project_phase:
+          item.dataValues.project_phase.dataValues.nm_project_phase,
+      };
+    });
+
+    const uniqueAddresses = Array.from(
+      new Set(getCoordinates.map(a => a.nm_project_phase))
+    ).map(id => {
+      return getCoordinates.find(a => a.nm_project_phase === id);
+    });
+
+    return {
+      projectPhases: uniqueAddresses,
+    };
+  }
+}

+import { TimelapseRepository } from '../../database/repositories';
+
+export class FindCoordinatesService {
+  async execute({ id_project_phase }) {
+    const repository = new TimelapseRepository();
+
+    const getCoordinates = await repository.findTimelapseByProjectPhaseId({
+      id_project_phase,
+    });
+
+    const coordinates = getCoordinates.map(
+      ({
+        id_timelapse_coordinates,
+        nu_latitude,
+        nu_longitude,
+        ds_coordinates,
+      }) => ({
+        id_timelapse_coordinates,
+        nu_latitude,
+        nu_longitude,
+        ds_coordinates,
+      })
+    );
+
+    return {
+      projectPhases: coordinates,
+    };
+  }
+}

diff --git a/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.container.tsx b/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.container.tsx
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..b04d43a
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.container.tsx
@@ -0,0 +1,144 @@
+import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react'
+import { MapContext } from 'context/mapContext'
+import { useHistory } from 'react-router-dom'
+import 'react-image-gallery/styles/css/image-gallery.css'
+import './styles.css'
+import { ProjectPhaseApi } from 'services/endpoints/projectPhase'
+import { TimelapseApi } from 'services/endpoints/timelapse'
+import { MediaTimelapseApi } from 'services/endpoints/mediaTimelapse'
+import DataWorkPresentation from './dataWork.presentation'
+
+const DataWorkContainer = () => {
+  const history = useHistory()
+  const [category, setIdCategory] = useState('')
+  const [coordinate, setCoordinate] = useState('')
+  const [projectPhases, setProjectPhases] = useState([])
+  const [coordinates, setCoordinates] = useState([])
+  const [medias, setMedias] = useState([])
+  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false)
+  const [interval, setIntervalo] = useState(100)
+  const [hasNoMedia, setHasNoMedia] = useState(false)
+
+  const {
+    project: {
+      id_project,
+      nm_project,
+      nm_category,
+      tx_description,
+      nm_city,
+      project_phase,
+      nu_latitude,
+      nu_longitude,
+      value,
+      nm_project_phase,
+      ds_coordinates,
+      id_timelapse_coordinates,
+    },
+  } = useContext(MapContext)
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    if (coordinate === '') return
+
+    setLoading(true)
+
+    MediaTimelapseApi.getMedias({
+      id_timelapse_coordinates: id_timelapse_coordinates || coordinate,
+    }).then((res) => {
+      setHasNoMedia(res.data.projectPhases.length === 0)
+
+      setMedias(res.data.projectPhases)
+
+      setLoading(false)
+    })
+  }, [coordinate])
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    setCoordinates([])
+    setMedias([])
+
+    if (!category) {
+      setIdCategory('')
+
+      return
+    }
+
+    if (category === '') {
+      setCoordinate('')
+      return
+    }
+
+    TimelapseApi.getCoordinates({
+      id_project_phase: category,
+    }).then((res) => {
+      const response = res.data.projectPhases.map(
+        ({
+          id_timelapse_coordinates,
+          nu_longitude,
+          nu_latitude,
+          ds_coordinates,
+        }) => {
+          return {
+            id_timelapse_coordinates,
+            nu_longitude,
+            nu_latitude,
+            ds_coordinates,
+          }
+        }
+      )
+
+      setHasNoMedia(response.length === 0)
+
+      setCoordinates(response)
+
+      setCoordinate(response[0].id_timelapse_coordinates)
+    })
+  }, [category])
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    ProjectPhaseApi.getProjectPhaseWithTimelapse({
+      id_project,
+    }).then((res) => {
+      setHasNoMedia(res.data.projectPhases.length === 0)
+
+      const response = res.data.projectPhases.map(
+        ({ id_project_phase, nm_project_phase }) => {
+          return {
+            id_project_phase,
+            nm_project_phase,
+          }
+        }
+      )
+
+      setProjectPhases(response)
+
+      setIdCategory(response.length > 0 ? response[0].id_project_phase : '')
+    })
+  }, [id_project])
+
+  return (
+    <DataWorkPresentation
+      hasNoMedia={hasNoMedia}
+      nm_project_phase={nm_project_phase}
+      ds_coordinates={ds_coordinates}
+      coordinates={coordinates}
+      setCoordinate={setCoordinate}
+      nm_project={nm_project}
+      projectPhases={projectPhases}
+      setIdCategory={setIdCategory}
+      loading={loading}
+      medias={medias}
+      setIntervalo={setIntervalo}
+      interval={interval}
+      history={history}
+      nm_category={nm_category}
+      tx_description={tx_description}
+      nm_city={nm_city}
+      project_phase={project_phase}
+      nu_latitude={nu_latitude}
+      nu_longitude={nu_longitude}
+      value={value}
+    />
+  )
+}
+
+export default DataWorkContainer
diff --git a/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.presentation.tsx b/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.presentation.tsx
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..6575949
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/containers/Map/DataWork/dataWork.presentation.tsx
@@ -0,0 +1,219 @@
+import React from 'react'
+// eslint-disable-next-line import/no-duplicates
+import ptLocale from 'date-fns/locale/pt-BR'
+import {
+  Container,
+  Timelapse,
+  Description,
+  ProjectName,
+  ProjectPhaseName,
+  DescriptionTitle,
+  DescriptionText,
+  CityTitle,
+  CityName,
+  Value,
+  BackButton,
+  Image,
+  SelectContainer,
+  Loading,
+  Interval,
+  TimelapseInfo,
+  SelectContent,
+  NoMedia,
+} from './dataWork.styles'
+import { Redirect } from 'react-router-dom'
+import { GrClose } from 'react-icons/gr'
+import 'react-image-gallery/styles/css/image-gallery.css'
+import ImageGallery from 'react-image-gallery'
+import './styles.css'
+// eslint-disable-next-line import/no-duplicates
+import { format } from 'date-fns'
+import { Select } from 'antd'
+import { MdOutlineErrorOutline } from 'react-icons/md'
+const { Option } = Select
+
+const DataWorkContainer = ({
+  coordinates,
+  setCoordinate,
+  nm_project,
+  projectPhases,
+  setIdCategory,
+  loading,
+  medias,
+  setIntervalo,
+  interval,
+  history,
+  nm_category,
+  tx_description,
+  nm_city,
+  project_phase,
+  nu_latitude,
+  nu_longitude,
+  value,
+  nm_project_phase,
+  ds_coordinates,
+  hasNoMedia,
+}) => {
+  return (
+    <>
+      {nm_project ? (
+        <Container>
+          <Timelapse>
+            {nm_project_phase && ds_coordinates ? (
+              <TimelapseInfo>
+                <p>
+                  <strong>Fase:</strong> {nm_project_phase}
+                </p>
+                <p>
+                  <strong>Coordenada:</strong> {ds_coordinates}
+                </p>
+              </TimelapseInfo>
+            ) : (
+              <SelectContainer>
+                {projectPhases.length > 0 && (
+                  <SelectContent>
+                    <strong>Fase:</strong>
+                    <Select
+                      onChange={(value) => setIdCategory(value)}
+                      placeholder="Selecione a Fase"
+                      onClear={() => setIdCategory('')}
+                      defaultValue={projectPhases[0].id_project_phase}
+                      style={{ width: 350, border: 0 }}>
+                      {projectPhases?.map(
+                        ({ id_project_phase, nm_project_phase }) => (
+                          <Option key={Math.random()} value={id_project_phase}>
+                            {nm_project_phase}
+                          </Option>
+                        )
+                      )}
+                    </Select>
+                  </SelectContent>
+                )}
+
+                {coordinates.length > 0 && (
+                  <SelectContent>
+                    <strong>Coordenada:</strong>
+                    <Select
+                      onChange={(value) => setCoordinate(value)}
+                      placeholder="Selecione a Coordernada"
+                      allowClear={true}
+                      defaultValue={coordinates[0].id_timelapse_coordinates}
+                      style={{ width: 350 }}>
+                      {coordinates?.map((item) => {
+                        return (
+                          <Option
+                            key={Math.random()}
+                            value={item.id_timelapse_coordinates}>
+                            {item.ds_coordinates}
+                          </Option>
+                        )
+                      })}
+                    </Select>
+                  </SelectContent>
+                )}
+
+                {coordinates.length === 0 && projectPhases.length > 0 && (
+                  <Select
+                    placeholder="Selecione a Fase primeiramente"
+                    allowClear={true}
+                    style={{ width: 350 }}>
+                    <Option value="">Selecione a Fase primeiramente</Option>
+                  </Select>
+                )}
+              </SelectContainer>
+            )}
+
+            {loading ? (
+              <Loading />
+            ) : (
+              <>
+                {medias.length > 0 ? (
+                  <>
+                    <ImageGallery
+                      slideInterval={0.5}
+                      flickThreshold={0.5}
+                      slideDuration={interval}
+                      showFullscreenButton={true}
+                      items={medias.map(({ dt_media, nm_file }) => ({
+                        original: `http://143.198.191.56:3030/v1/api/ger-obras//media_timelapse/download/${nm_file}`,
+
+                        description: format(
+                          new Date(dt_media),
+                          "dd 'de' MMMM 'de' yyyy",
+                          {
+                            locale: ptLocale,
+                          }
+                        ),
+                      }))}
+                    />
+
+                    <Interval>
+                      <div>
+                        <button
+                          onClick={() =>
+                            setIntervalo((oldState) =>
+                              oldState === 0 ? 0 : oldState - 100
+                            )
+                          }>
+                          -
+                        </button>
+                        <input type="number" value={interval} readOnly />
+                        <button
+                          onClick={() =>
+                            setIntervalo((oldState) =>
+                              oldState === 0 ? 100 : oldState + 100
+                            )
+                          }>
+                          +
+                        </button>
+                      </div>
+                      <small>Velocidade de reprodução: {interval}ms</small>
+                    </Interval>
+                  </>
+                ) : (
+                  <>
+                    {hasNoMedia && (
+                      <NoMedia>
+                        <MdOutlineErrorOutline size={200} />
+                        <h1>Não há imagens a serem exibidas!!</h1>
+                      </NoMedia>
+                    )}
+                  </>
+                )}
+              </>
+            )}
+          </Timelapse>
+          <Description>
+            <BackButton onClick={() => history.push('obras')} title="Voltar">
+              <GrClose size={30} />
+            </BackButton>
+            <ProjectName>{nm_project}</ProjectName>
+            <ProjectPhaseName>{nm_category}</ProjectPhaseName>
+            <DescriptionTitle>Descrição</DescriptionTitle>
+            <DescriptionText>
+              {tx_description || 'Não Possui descrição'}
+            </DescriptionText>
+            <CityTitle>Município</CityTitle>
+            <CityName>{nm_city}</CityName>
+            <CityTitle>Fase atual do projeto</CityTitle>
+            <CityName>{project_phase || 'Não iniciado'}</CityName>
+
+            <CityTitle>Coordenadas</CityTitle>
+            <CityName>
+              <strong>Latitude:</strong> {nu_latitude}{' '}
+              <strong>Longitude:</strong>
+              {nu_longitude}
+            </CityName>
+
+            <CityTitle>Valor da obra</CityTitle>
+            <Value>R$ {value}</Value>
+          </Description>
+        </Container>
+      ) : (
+        <Redirect to="obras" />
+      )}
+    </>
+  )
+}
+
+export default DataWorkContainer

+import React, { useEffect, useState, useContext } from 'react'
+import './App.css'
+import { MapApi } from 'services/endpoints/map'
+import swel from 'sweetalert2'
+import useCategory from 'hooks/select/useCategory'
+import MapPresentation from './map.presentation'
+import { MapContext } from 'context/mapContext'
+
+export default function App() {
+  const { coordinates, setCoordinates } = useContext(MapContext)
+
+  const [nmProject, setNmProject] = useState('')
+  const [nm_city, setNmCity] = useState('')
+  const [id_category, setIdCategory] = useState('')
+  const [tp_project_phase, setPhase] = useState('')
+
+  const [userLatitude, setUserLatitude] = useState(-22.979718)
+  const [userLongitude, setUserLongitude] = useState(-43.23351)
+
+  const [getData, setGetData] = useState(false)
+
+  const [projectInfo, setProjectInfo] = useState([])
+
+  const [timelapseLoading, setTimelapseLoading] = useState(false)
+
+  const categories = useCategory()
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition((position) => {
+      setUserLatitude(position.coords.latitude)
+      setUserLongitude(position.coords.longitude)
+    })
+  }, [])
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    setProjectInfo([])
+
+    MapApi.GetProjectData({ id_location: getData }).then((res) => {
+      setProjectInfo([res.data.projects])
+    })
+  }, [getData])
+
+  useEffect(() => {
+    if (coordinates.length > 0) return
+
+    swel.fire({
+      text: 'Carregando obras...',
+      showConfirmButton: false,
+      didOpen: async () => {
+        swel.showLoading()
+
+        await MapApi.GetCoordinates().then((res) => {
+          setCoordinates(res.data.projects)
+          swel.close()
+        })
+      },
+    })
+  }, [])
+
+  // useEffect(() => {
+  //   swel.fire({
+  //     text: 'Buscando projetos B...',
+  //     showConfirmButton: false,
+  //     didOpen: async () => {
+  //       swel.showLoading()
+  //       await MapApi.GetPortfolios({
+  //         nm_project: nmProject,
+  //         nm_city,
+  //         tp_project_phase,

+  //           swel.fire({
+  //             icon: 'error',
+  //             width: 'auto',
+  //             text: 'Não há nenhum Projeto que atenda as opções de filtro informadas',
+  //           })
+  //           return
+  //         }
+
+  //         setProjects(res.data.projects)
+  //         swel.close()
+  //       })
+  //     },
+  //   })
+  // }, [id_category])
+
+  // useEffect(() => {
+  //   swel.fire({
+  //     text: 'Buscando projetos C...',
+  //     showConfirmButton: false,
+  //     didOpen: async () => {
+  //       swel.showLoading()

+  //         nm_project: nmProject,
+  //         nm_city,

+  //         id_category,
+  //       }).then((res) => {
+  //         if (res.data.projects.length === 0) {
+  //           swel.fire({
+  //             icon: 'error',
+  //             width: 'auto',
+  //             text: 'Não há nenhum Projeto que atenda as opções de filtro informadas',
+  //           })
+  //           return
+  //         }
+
+  //         setProjects(res.data.projects)
+  //         swel.close()
+  //       })
+  //     },
+  //   })
+  // }, [tp_project_phase])
+
+  const handleSearch = () => {
+    setCoordinates([])
+    swel.fire({
+      text: 'Carregando obras...',
+      showConfirmButton: false,
+      didOpen: async () => {
+        swel.showLoading()
+        await MapApi.GetPortfolios({
+          nm_project: nmProject,
+          nm_city,
+          tp_project_phase,
+          id_category,
+        }).then((res) => {
+          if (res.data.projects.length === 0) {
+            swel.fire({
+              icon: 'error',
+              width: 'auto',
+              text: 'Não há nenhum Projeto que atenda as opções de filtro informadas',
+            })
+            return
+          }
+
+          setCoordinates(res.data.projects)
+          swel.close()
+        })
+      },
+    })
+  }
+
+  const handleClose = async () => {
+    setCoordinates([])
+    setNmProject('')
+    setNmCity('')
+  }
+
+  return (
+    <MapPresentation
+      setTimelapseLoading={setTimelapseLoading}
+      timelapseLoading={timelapseLoading}
+      coordinates={coordinates}
+      projectInfo={projectInfo}
+      setGetData={setGetData}
+      getData={getData}
+      userLongitude={userLongitude}
+      userLatitude={userLatitude}
+      handleSearch={handleSearch}
+      setNmProject={setNmProject}
+      nmProject={nmProject}
+      handleClose={handleClose}
+      projects={coordinates}
+      setNmCity={setNmCity}
+      nm_city={nm_city}
+      setIdCategory={setIdCategory}
+      categories={categories}
+      setPhase={setPhase}
+    />
+  )
+}

+import { api } from '../api'
+
+export const MapApi = {
+  GetProjectTimelapse: async ({ id_timelapse_coordinates }) => {
+    return await api.get(
+      `/map/projects/timelapse?id_timelapse_coordinates=${id_timelapse_coordinates}`
+    )
+  },
+  GetProjectData: async ({ id_location }) => {
+    return await api.get(`/map/projects/location?id_location=${id_location}`)
+  },
+  GetCoordinates: async () => {
+    return await api.get(`/map/projects/coordinates`)
+  },
+  GetPortfolios: async ({
+    nm_project,
+    nm_city,
+    tp_project_phase,
+    id_category,
+  }: {
+    nm_project?: string
+    nm_city?: string
+    tp_project_phase?: string
+    id_category?: string
+  }) => {
+    return await api.get(
+      `/map/projects?ex=1${nm_project ? `&nm_project=${nm_project}` : ''}${
+        nm_city ? `&nm_city=${nm_city}` : ''
+      }${tp_project_phase ? `&tp_project_phase=${tp_project_phase}` : ''}${
+        id_category ? `&id_category=${id_category}` : ''
+      }`
+    )
+  },
+}
